{"tid":213532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來廢老自殺率都幾高下","createTime":"2017-04-23T07:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T09:21:54.000Z","uid":109889,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4c5c2a1ac8dcfaf2d55c585bba06231125d56a4","tid":213532,"uid":109889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"香港的長者自殺率是本地各年齡組別中最高的，達每年十萬人中有三十個案例以上，是青少年自殺率的十倍。本地的長者自殺率也較諸大多西方各國高出三倍以上。事實上，香港每三個自殺者中即有一人為長者，當中男女的比例相若。長者自殺的總數也很可能會隨著本地人口老化而逐年遞增。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ha.org.hk/espp/suicide.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ha.org.hk%2Fespp%2Fsuicide.html&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=9c67dc03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ha.org.hk/espp/suicide.html</a>"},{"pid":"967565f2f6f64019ad028a6da781adaa509262af","tid":213532,"uid":84354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:59:46.000Z","msg":"好唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23580a385c8e1bc568649cf60259d653d9930522","tid":213532,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:04:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25386970a9c747d12b4d4f94b6091816944a97d3","tid":213532,"uid":109903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:12:37.000Z","msg":"點解又冇人話班廢老AQ低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d149e224efd347c26d15dae5789464b11a895a73","tid":213532,"uid":109889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老幼齊齊死"},{"pid":"53283cafbbb9a57b323eb40014a1514a7c844768","tid":213532,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁咪識諗囉</bl